      • queryPost

        @Headers(value="Content-Type:application/json")
 @POST(value="api/v2/query")
retrofit2.Call<String> queryPost(@Header(value="Zap-Trace-Span")
                                                                                                              String zapTraceSpan,
                                                                                                              @Header(value="Accept")
                                                                                                              String accept,
                                                                                                              @Header(value="Content-Type")
                                                                                                              String contentType,
                                                                                                              @Query(value="org")
                                                                                                              String org,
                                                                                                              @Query(value="orgID")
                                                                                                              String orgID,
                                                                                                              @Body
                                                                                                              Query query)
        query an influx
        Parameters:
        zapTraceSpan - OpenTracing span context (optional)
        accept - specifies the return content format. Each response content type will have its own dialect options. (optional, default to text/csv)
        contentType - (optional)
        org - specifies the name of the organization executing the query; if both orgID and org are specified, orgID takes precendence. (optional)
        orgID - specifies the ID of the organization executing the query; if both orgID and org are specified, orgID takes precendence. (optional)
        query - flux query or specification to execute (optional)
        Returns:
        Call<String>
